		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Three-component video can be 240p too. Vs. System is 240p RGB. PlayChoice is 240p RGB. And on a Wii set to 480i (not 480p) mode, 8- and 16-bit VC games through a component cable are 240p YPrPb.

		

